## Goal
Generate pre-computed analytics data files (statistics.json, timeline.json, etc.) during export that enable instant dashboard rendering in the browser without expensive SQL aggregations.

## Why This Task is Important

Section 9.2.1 of the plan specifies pre-computed data files:
- Instant dashboard rendering (no SQL on load)
- Reduces sqlite-wasm memory pressure
- Enables rich visualizations
- Data is encrypted alongside the database

